# Components

- Prefer Server Components by default.
- Use Client Components only for browser APIs, state, or event handlers.
- Keep business logic outside UI components.
- Prefer composition over deep nesting.

```tsx
// ❌ BAD — client component for static content
"use client";
export function Title() { return <h1>Hello</h1>; }

// ✅ GOOD — server component unless interactivity is needed
export function Title() { return <h1>Hello</h1>; }
```
